<br>
Thankfully, he seems to be unstoppable at 13 (or doesn't it always seem that way when you are at the lower levels?) and regen is great.  Most his weapons skills are maxxed out (sans the blunt weapons) and may he eventually get some nicer weapons later in his career.  Also, how good is bash to build up?  I've been maxxing the skill out every level just in case, but how often do you end up using it in your daily hunting?  At any rate, thanks all for the insight.<br>
<br>
Notechis<br>
Level 13 Iksar Warrior<br>
